---
description: pylib subsystem
globs: pylib/anki/**
alwaysApply: false
---
When working under pylib/anki, read pylib/anki/CLAUDE.md for local detail — it
is the single source of truth for this Python<->Rust seam.
Key gotcha: `RustBackendGenerated` is auto-generated at build time to
out/pylib/anki/_backend_generated.py and is not in the source tree, so imports
fail unless the build is complete (run `just pylib`).
